items.summary: Add the missing generated favicon image file to the frontend static assets at frontend/public/assets/generated/subrin-favicon-uploaded.dim_32x32.png so the browser can load the favicon instead of falling back to the default tab icon.

Ensure frontend/index.html references the correct favicon path and filename: /assets/generated/subrin-favicon-uploaded.dim_32x32.png (type image/png, sizes 32x32). Update it only if it does not exactly match the generated asset filename/path.
